sequenceDiagram
    participant U1 as Tab 1
    participant S as Socket.IO Server
    participant G as game-service
    participant R as Redis
    participant U2 as Tab 2 / Tab 3

    U1->>S: connect
    S->>G: create/connect player
    G->>R: save player state
    S-->>U1: updatePlayers

    U1->>S: move(direction, seq)
    S->>G: validate + rate limit
    G->>R: update position
    G-->>S: move applied
    S-->>U1: moveAck
    S-->>U2: playerMoved / updatePlayers
